{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm standing in front of you today"},{"time":4000,"text":"in all humility,"},{"time":6000,"text":"wanting to share with you"},{"time":8000,"text":"my journey of the last six years"},{"time":11000,"text":"in the field of service"},{"time":13000,"text":"and education."},{"time":15000,"text":"And I'm not a trained academic."},{"time":18000,"text":"Neither am I a veteran social worker."},{"time":21000,"text":"I was 26 years in the corporate world,"},{"time":24000,"text":"trying to make organizations profitable."},{"time":27000,"text":"And then in 2003"},{"time":29000,"text":"I started Parikrma Humanity Foundation"},{"time":33000,"text":"from my kitchen table."}]},{"cues":[{"time":35000,"text":"The first thing that we did was walk through the slums."},{"time":39000,"text":"You know, by the way, there are two million people"},{"time":42000,"text":"in Bangalore, who live in 800 slums."},{"time":47000,"text":"We couldn't go to all the slums,"},{"time":50000,"text":"but we tried to cover as much as we could."},{"time":52000,"text":"We walked through these slums,"},{"time":54000,"text":"identified houses where children would never go to school."},{"time":59000,"text":"We talked to the parents,"},{"time":61000,"text":"tried to convince them about sending their children to school."},{"time":65000,"text":"We played with the children,"},{"time":67000,"text":"and came back home really tired,"},{"time":70000,"text":"exhausted, but with images"},{"time":73000,"text":"of bright faces, twinkling eyes,"},{"time":76000,"text":"and went to sleep."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79000,"text":"We were all excited to start,"},{"time":82000,"text":"but the numbers hit us then:"},{"time":86000,"text":"200 million children"},{"time":88000,"text":"between four to 14 that"},{"time":90000,"text":"should be going to school, but do not;"},{"time":92000,"text":"100 million children"},{"time":94000,"text":"who go to school but cannot read;"},{"time":97000,"text":"125 million who cannot do basic maths."},{"time":102000,"text":"We also heard that 250 billion Indian rupees"},{"time":107000,"text":"was dedicated for government schooling."},{"time":110000,"text":"Ninety percent of it was spent on teachers' salary"},{"time":113000,"text":"and administrators' salary."},{"time":115000,"text":"And yet, India has nearly"},{"time":117000,"text":"the highest teacher absenteeism"},{"time":120000,"text":"in the world,"},{"time":122000,"text":"with one out of four teachers"},{"time":124000,"text":"not going to school at all the entire academic year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128000,"text":"Those numbers were absolutely mind-boggling,"},{"time":132000,"text":"overwhelming, and we were constantly asked,"},{"time":135000,"text":"\"When will you start? How many schools will you start?"},{"time":138000,"text":"How many children will you get?"},{"time":140000,"text":"How are you going to scale?"},{"time":142000,"text":"How are you going to replicate?\""},{"time":144000,"text":"It was very difficult not to get scared, not to get daunted."},{"time":148000,"text":"But we dug our heels"},{"time":150000,"text":"and said, \"We're not in the number game."},{"time":153000,"text":"We want to take one child at a time"},{"time":157000,"text":"and take the child right through school,"},{"time":160000,"text":"sent to college,"},{"time":162000,"text":"and get them prepared for better living,"},{"time":166000,"text":"a high value job.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":169000,"text":"So, we started Parikrma."},{"time":172000,"text":"The first Parikrma school"},{"time":174000,"text":"started in a slum"},{"time":176000,"text":"where there were 70,000 people"},{"time":179000,"text":"living below the poverty line."},{"time":182000,"text":"Our first school was"},{"time":185000,"text":"on a rooftop of a building inside the slums,"},{"time":190000,"text":"a second story building, the only second story building"},{"time":192000,"text":"inside the slums."},{"time":194000,"text":"And that rooftop did not have"},{"time":197000,"text":"any ceiling, only half a tin sheet."},{"time":201000,"text":"That was our first school. One hundred sixty-five children."},{"time":205000,"text":"Indian academic year begins in June."},{"time":207000,"text":"So, June it rains, so many a times"},{"time":210000,"text":"all of us would be huddled under the tin roof,"},{"time":213000,"text":"waiting for the rain to stop."},{"time":215000,"text":"My God! What a bonding exercise that was."},{"time":220000,"text":"And all of us"},{"time":222000,"text":"that were under that roof are still here together today."},{"time":226000,"text":"Then came the second school,"},{"time":228000,"text":"the third school, the fourth school"},{"time":231000,"text":"and a junior college."},{"time":233000,"text":"In six years now,"},{"time":236000,"text":"we have four schools, one junior college,"},{"time":239000,"text":"1,100 children"},{"time":241000,"text":"coming from 28 slums"},{"time":243000,"text":"and four orphanages."},{"time":245000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":248000,"text":"Our dream is very simple:"},{"time":251000,"text":"to send each of these kids, get them prepared"},{"time":254000,"text":"to be educated"},{"time":257000,"text":"but also to live peacefully,"},{"time":259000,"text":"contented in this conflict-ridden"},{"time":262000,"text":"chaotic globalized world."},{"time":266000,"text":"Now, when you talk global"},{"time":268000,"text":"you have to talk English."},{"time":270000,"text":"And so all our schools"},{"time":272000,"text":"are English medium schools."},{"time":275000,"text":"But they know there is this myth"},{"time":277000,"text":"that children from the slums"},{"time":279000,"text":"cannot speak English well."},{"time":282000,"text":"No one in their family has spoken English."},{"time":284000,"text":"No one in their generation has spoken English."},{"time":288000,"text":"But how wrong it is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290000,"text":"Girl: I like adventurous books, and some of my favorites"},{"time":293000,"text":"are Alfred Hitchcock and [unclear]"},{"time":297000,"text":"and Hardy Boys."},{"time":299000,"text":"Although they are like"},{"time":301000,"text":"in different contexts,"},{"time":303000,"text":"one is magical, the other two are like investigation,"},{"time":306000,"text":"I like those books because"},{"time":309000,"text":"they have something special in them."},{"time":311000,"text":"The vocabulary used in those books"},{"time":313000,"text":"and the style of writing."},{"time":316000,"text":"I mean like once I pick up one book"},{"time":318000,"text":"I cannot put it down until I finish the whole book."},{"time":321000,"text":"Even if it takes me four and a half hours,"},{"time":323000,"text":"or three and half hours to finish my book, I do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326000,"text":"Boy: I did good research and I got the information"},{"time":329000,"text":"[on the] world's fastest cars."},{"time":332000,"text":"I like Ducati ZZ143,"},{"time":338000,"text":"because it is the fastest,"},{"time":340000,"text":"the world's fastest bike,"},{"time":342000,"text":"and I like Pulsar 220 DTSI"},{"time":346000,"text":"because it is India's fastest bike. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":349000,"text":"Shukla Bose: Well, that girl that you saw,"},{"time":353000,"text":"her father sells flowers on the roadside."},{"time":356000,"text":"And this little boy has been coming to school for five years."},{"time":360000,"text":"But isn't it strange that little boys all over the world"},{"time":364000,"text":"love fast bikes? (Laughter)"},{"time":367000,"text":"He hasn't seen one, he hasn't ridden one, of course,"},{"time":370000,"text":"but he has done a lot of research through Google search."},{"time":375000,"text":"You know, when we started with our English medium schools"},{"time":378000,"text":"we also decided to adopt"},{"time":380000,"text":"the best curriculum possible,"},{"time":382000,"text":"the ICSE curriculum."},{"time":384000,"text":"And again, there were people who laughed at me"},{"time":387000,"text":"and said, \"Don't be crazy"},{"time":389000,"text":"choosing such a tough curriculum for these students."},{"time":392000,"text":"They'll never be able to cope.\""},{"time":394000,"text":"Not only do our children cope very well,"},{"time":397000,"text":"but they excel in it."},{"time":399000,"text":"You should just come across to see"},{"time":401000,"text":"how well our children do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404000,"text":"There is also this myth that"},{"time":406000,"text":"parents from the slums"},{"time":409000,"text":"are not interested in their children going to school;"},{"time":412000,"text":"they'd much rather put them to work."},{"time":414000,"text":"That's absolute hogwash."},{"time":416000,"text":"All parents all over the world"},{"time":418000,"text":"want their children to lead a better life than themselves,"},{"time":422000,"text":"but they need to believe that change is possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427000,"text":"Video: (Hindi)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":463000,"text":"SB: We have 80 percent attendance"},{"time":466000,"text":"for all our parents-teachers meeting."},{"time":468000,"text":"Sometimes it's even 100 percent,"},{"time":470000,"text":"much more than many privileged schools."},{"time":473000,"text":"Fathers have started to attend."},{"time":475000,"text":"It's very interesting. When we started our school"},{"time":478000,"text":"the parents would give thumbprints in the attendance register."},{"time":483000,"text":"Now they have started writing their signature."},{"time":487000,"text":"The children have taught them."},{"time":489000,"text":"It's amazing how much children can teach."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493000,"text":"We have, a few months ago,"},{"time":496000,"text":"actually late last year,"},{"time":498000,"text":"we had a few mothers who came to us and said,"},{"time":500000,"text":"\"You know, we want to learn how to read and write."},{"time":504000,"text":"Can you teach us?\" So, we started an afterschool"},{"time":507000,"text":"for our parents, for our mothers."},{"time":509000,"text":"We had 25 mothers who came regularly"},{"time":511000,"text":"after school to study."},{"time":514000,"text":"We want to continue with this program"},{"time":516000,"text":"and extend it to all our other schools."}]},{"cues":[{"time":520000,"text":"Ninety-eight percent of our fathers are alcoholics."},{"time":523000,"text":"So, you can imagine how traumatized"},{"time":525000,"text":"and how dysfunctional the houses are where our children come from."},{"time":529000,"text":"We have to send the fathers to de-addiction labs"},{"time":534000,"text":"and when they come back,"},{"time":536000,"text":"most times sober, we have to find a job for them"},{"time":540000,"text":"so that they don't regress."},{"time":542000,"text":"We have about three fathers who have been trained to cook."},{"time":546000,"text":"We have taught them nutrition, hygiene."},{"time":551000,"text":"We have helped them set up the kitchen"},{"time":553000,"text":"and now they are supplying food to all our children."},{"time":556000,"text":"They do a very good job because"},{"time":559000,"text":"their children are eating their food,"},{"time":561000,"text":"but most importantly this is the first time"},{"time":563000,"text":"they have got respect,"},{"time":565000,"text":"and they feel that they are doing something worthwhile."}]},{"cues":[{"time":569000,"text":"More than 90 percent of our non-teaching staff"},{"time":572000,"text":"are all parents and extended families."},{"time":576000,"text":"We've started many programs"},{"time":578000,"text":"just to make sure that the child comes to school."},{"time":582000,"text":"Vocational skill program for the older siblings"},{"time":585000,"text":"so the younger ones are not stopped from coming to school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":589000,"text":"There is also this myth that children from the slums"},{"time":592000,"text":"cannot integrate with mainstream."},{"time":596000,"text":"Take a look at this little girl"},{"time":598000,"text":"who was one of the 28 children"},{"time":601000,"text":"from all privileged schools,"},{"time":603000,"text":"best schools in the country"},{"time":605000,"text":"that was selected for the Duke University"},{"time":608000,"text":"talent identification program"},{"time":610000,"text":"and was sent to IIM Ahmedabad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":613000,"text":"Video: Girl: Duke IIMA Camp. Whenever we see that IIMA,"},{"time":616000,"text":"it was such a pride for us to go to that camp."},{"time":619000,"text":"Everybody was very friendly,"},{"time":622000,"text":"especially I got a lot of friends."},{"time":625000,"text":"And I felt that my English has improved a lot"},{"time":627000,"text":"going there and chatting with friends."},{"time":630000,"text":"There they met children who are"},{"time":634000,"text":"with a different standard and"},{"time":638000,"text":"a different mindset, a totally different society."},{"time":641000,"text":"I mingled with almost everyone."},{"time":644000,"text":"They were very friendly."},{"time":646000,"text":"I had very good friends there,"},{"time":648000,"text":"who are from Delhi, who are from Mumbai."},{"time":652000,"text":"Even now we are in touch through Facebook."}]},{"cues":[{"time":656000,"text":"After this Ahmedabad trip"},{"time":660000,"text":"I've been like a totally different"},{"time":663000,"text":"mingling with people and all of those."},{"time":665000,"text":"Before that I feel like I wasn't like this."},{"time":668000,"text":"I don't even mingle, or start speaking with someone so quickly."},{"time":672000,"text":"My accent with English improved a lot."},{"time":677000,"text":"And I learned football, volleyball,"},{"time":680000,"text":"Frisbee, lots of games."},{"time":682000,"text":"And I wouldn't want to go to Bangalore. Let me stay here."},{"time":685000,"text":"Such beautiful food,"},{"time":687000,"text":"I enjoyed it. It was so beautiful."},{"time":690000,"text":"I enjoyed eating food like"},{"time":692000,"text":"[unclear] would come and ask me,"},{"time":697000,"text":"\"Yes ma'am, what you want?\" It was so good to hear!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":699000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":701000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":705000,"text":"SB: This girl was working as a maid"},{"time":707000,"text":"before she came to school."},{"time":709000,"text":"And today she wants to be a neurologist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":713000,"text":"Our children are doing brilliantly in sports."},{"time":717000,"text":"They are really excelling."},{"time":719000,"text":"There is an inter-school athletic competition"},{"time":722000,"text":"that is held every year"},{"time":725000,"text":"in Bangalore, where 5,000 children participate"},{"time":729000,"text":"from 140 best schools in the city."},{"time":732000,"text":"We've got the best school award for three years successively."},{"time":739000,"text":"And our children are coming back home"},{"time":741000,"text":"with bags full of medals, with lots of admirers and friends."},{"time":745000,"text":"Last year there were a couple of kids"},{"time":749000,"text":"from elite schools that came"},{"time":751000,"text":"to ask for admissions in our school."},{"time":753000,"text":"We also have our very own dream team."}]},{"cues":[{"time":758000,"text":"Why is this happening? Why this confidence?"},{"time":760000,"text":"Is it the exposure? We have professors"},{"time":764000,"text":"from MIT, Berkeley, Stanford,"},{"time":767000,"text":"Indian Institute of Science"},{"time":769000,"text":"who come and teach our children lots of scientific formulas,"},{"time":773000,"text":"experiments, much beyond the classroom."},{"time":776000,"text":"Art, music are considered"},{"time":779000,"text":"therapy and mediums of expression."},{"time":783000,"text":"We also believe that"},{"time":786000,"text":"it's the content that is more important."},{"time":790000,"text":"It is not the infrastructure,"},{"time":794000,"text":"not the toilets, not the libraries,"},{"time":797000,"text":"but it is what actually happens in this school"},{"time":800000,"text":"that is more important."},{"time":802000,"text":"Creating an environment of learning,"},{"time":805000,"text":"of inquiry, of exploration"},{"time":808000,"text":"is what is true education."}]},{"cues":[{"time":810000,"text":"When we started Parikrma"},{"time":812000,"text":"we had no idea which direction we were taking."},{"time":815000,"text":"We didn't hire McKinsey to do a business plan."},{"time":818000,"text":"But we know for sure that"},{"time":821000,"text":"what we want to do today is"},{"time":825000,"text":"take one child at a time,"},{"time":827000,"text":"not get bogged with numbers,"},{"time":829000,"text":"and actually see the child complete"},{"time":833000,"text":"the circle of life,"},{"time":835000,"text":"and unleash his total potential."},{"time":839000,"text":"We do not believe in scale"},{"time":843000,"text":"because we believe in quality,"},{"time":845000,"text":"and scale and numbers will automatically happen."},{"time":849000,"text":"We have corporates that have stood behind us,"},{"time":852000,"text":"and we are able to, now, open more schools."},{"time":855000,"text":"But we began with the idea"},{"time":857000,"text":"of one child at a time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":859000,"text":"This is five-year-old Parusharam."},{"time":862000,"text":"He was begging"},{"time":864000,"text":"by a bus stop a few years ago,"},{"time":866000,"text":"got picked up and is now in an orphanage,"},{"time":869000,"text":"has been coming to school for the last four and a half months."},{"time":873000,"text":"He's in kindergarten."},{"time":875000,"text":"He has learned how to speak English."},{"time":877000,"text":"We have a model by which kids can speak English"},{"time":880000,"text":"and understand English"},{"time":882000,"text":"in three month's time."},{"time":884000,"text":"He can tell you stories in English"},{"time":887000,"text":"of the thirsty crow, of the crocodile"},{"time":889000,"text":"and of the giraffe."},{"time":891000,"text":"And if you ask him what he likes to do"},{"time":893000,"text":"he will say, \"I like sleeping."},{"time":895000,"text":"I like eating. I like playing.\""},{"time":898000,"text":"And if you ask him what he wants to do,"},{"time":900000,"text":"he will say, \"I want to horsing.\""},{"time":902000,"text":"Now, \"horsing\" is going for a horse ride."},{"time":905000,"text":"So, Parusharam comes to my office every day."},{"time":908000,"text":"He comes for a tummy rub,"},{"time":911000,"text":"because he believes that will give me luck. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":913000,"text":"When I started Parikrma"},{"time":916000,"text":"I began with a great deal of arrogance"},{"time":920000,"text":"of transforming the world."},{"time":922000,"text":"But today I have been transformed."},{"time":925000,"text":"I have been changed with my children."},{"time":927000,"text":"I've learned so much from them:"},{"time":930000,"text":"love, compassion, imagination"},{"time":933000,"text":"and such creativity."},{"time":936000,"text":"Parusharam is Parikrma"},{"time":940000,"text":"with a simple beginning but a long way to go."},{"time":943000,"text":"I promise you, Parusharam"},{"time":945000,"text":"will speak in the TED conference a few years from now."},{"time":949000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":951000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}